NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::ApocalypseTests - Creates the Test::Apocalypse
    testfile for Dist::Zilla

VERSION
      This document describes v1.000 of Dist::Zilla::Plugin::ApocalypseTests - released December 13, 2010 as part of Dist-Zilla-Plugin-ApocalypseTests.

DESCRIPTION
    This is an extension of Dist::Zilla::Plugin::InlineFiles, providing the
    following files:

    *   t/apocalypse.t - Runs the dist through Test::Apocalypse

        For more information on what the test does, please look at
        Test::Apocalypse.

                # In your dist.ini:
                [ApocalypseTests]

ATTRIBUTES
  allow
    This option will be passed directly to Test::Apocalypse to control which
    sub-tests you want to run.

    The default is nothing.

  deny
    This option will be passed directly to Test::Apocalypse to control which
    sub-tests you want to run.

    The default is nothing.

